title: Apples News arrives in the UK with iOS 9.1 update
text:
Apple's News arrives in the UK with iOS 9.1 update 
The Telegraph Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
The Telegraph, Financial Times and Cond? Nast are among the UK launch partner publishers for the app, which has been designed as a solution to a fragmented news reading experience generated by hopping between apps or mobile sites....
